%^YELLOW%^Skill: Survival

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's survival skill indicates their understanding of life in the wilderness. It affects abilities such as tracking, and the ability to gather natural materials from one's surroundings, such as food and hides.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^wisdom
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^tracking, skinning, foraging

